A few things that can't be automated:

Remove 'ctl+shift+e' keybinding conflict
https://github.com/Microsoft/vscode/issues/48480#issuecomment-414464079

1. go to terminal type 'ibus-setup'
2. go to Emoji tab, press the '...' next to Emoji choice to get 'select keyboard shortcut for switching' window
3. use the delete button to delete the shortcut and leave nothing there, press OK
4. Close
